name: Homie
description:
I want to show how skateboarding scene in Yogyakarta - Indonesia looks like, i took this one when they feel confused seeking another spot for a new clip, this is a skateboarding crew from @/ ktbr.yk
i personally really like this photo a LOT because I love seeing people doing what they love or talking about something they are really passionate about. The reason why I love this is because you can see it in their faces, their eyes, they have a special shine, and I think that's the most beautiful thing in the world
